    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine dei amen. Breve descriptis causam memorie quod aliquanti homines
                        de <placeName ref="#places/3200"
                            key="#Rivers #Kilns #Bridges/pontoons #Monasteries">Ficeclo</placeName>
                        in dei nomine iuraverunt a sancta dei evangelia, bona fide sine fraude daret
                        (â€¦)torium <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3209" key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                            >(opere) <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons">pontis</rs> de Ficeclo</orgName>
                        sive nostra pecunia expendenda a <rs key="#Kilns">furnacem</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> que est in
                            campo<orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3200" key="#Monasteries">
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">abatie</rs></orgName> usque a salina et non
                        haberimus in consilio vel factu quo pons destruatur vel contrarietur. Et si
                        quo tempore pons vi atque aliquo modo destructus fuerit, non interdicemus
                        eum non redificari, immo adiuvabimus ut reedificetur. Et nos in aliquo
                        tempore non erimus in consilio vel factu quod passipedium ad pontem <rs
                            key="#Rivers">Arni</rs> vel super ponte Arni inponatur vel auferatur,
                        vel ibi imponeretur. Et si impositum ibi fuerit, faciemus remanere, bona
                        fide, mercede petendo. Et non dabimus consilium vel adiutorium ullo modo in
                        danietate ipsius pontis vel eius operibus. Scilicet <persName><name
                                ref="Torpinus">Torpinus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rolandi</name></persName>, <persName
                            ref="#people/3238">Guido</persName> et <persName ref="#people/3239"
                            >Rolandinus</persName> germani et quondam <persName key="#Viscount"
                            ref="#people/3230">Ugonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs>, <persName><name ref="Ramo"
                                >Ramone</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Heinricus Gualandi">Enrigi Gualandi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Forestanus">Forestani</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> germani et
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gherardinus">Gerardini</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Duca">Duca</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Parens">Parent</name></persName> germani et quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Cecconerlus">Cechinerli</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Godolinus">Getholinus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Rustichellus">Rustichelli</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Hughicio">Uguicione</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Widoctus">Guidocto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolinus</name></persName> germani
                        et quondam <persName><name ref="Perutius">Perucci</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Greppaldus">Greppaldus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Assalitus">Assaliti</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Enrigus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Tollecta">Tollecte</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Widaloctus">Guidoloctus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName> germani et
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Robertus">Ruberti</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Sigismundus">Sesmondellus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Alioctus">Alioctus</name></persName> germani et
                        quondam <persName>Pylosichi</persName>, <persName><name ref="Amadeus"
                                >Amadeus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Deusdedit"
                                >Deodatus</name></persName> germani et quondam filii <persName><name
                                ref="Tholomaeus">Tolomi</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Hughicio">Ugicione</name></persName> cambiatori,
                                <persName><name ref="Leonardus">Leonardus</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Vetulus">Vetuli</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Tiniosus/Accarinus">Tiniosus
                            Accarini</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Hugolinus"
                                >Ugolini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Baroncellus"
                                >Baroncelli</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Paganus"
                                >Paganellus</name></persName>
                        <name ref="Treppo">Trepponis</name>, <persName><name ref="Matheus"
                                >Matheus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Draco"
                                >Drachi</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Stavalle"
                                >Stavalle</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Danitius"
                                >Danitti</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Rodelandus"
                                >Rolandinus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Frisingus">Fresingi</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandino</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Oddo">Oddi</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Armatus">Armati</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Teudaldus">Tedaldini</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Gotefredus">Gottifredus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Brunectus">Brunetti</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Avenante">Abenante</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wizo">Guittonis</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Robertus">Ruberto</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolinelli</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Deotisalvi">Deotisalvi</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Wizo">Guittonis</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus Cairi">Petrus Cairi</name></persName>,
                        Guisalbertus notarius, *** quondam <persName><name ref="Ormannus"
                                >Ormanni</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Ardingus"
                                >Ardinigellus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Imbrigatus">Imbrigati</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Usasinus">Usasini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ansidrus">Ansidri</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Hubaldus">Ugobaldus</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Godolinus">Getholini</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Trinciaullia">Trinciaullia</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bastardus">Bastardi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus de Orbignano">Martinellus</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/3238">Orbignano</placeName></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Capricius">Capricio</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Russo">Russi</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Deotifece">Deotifeci</name></persName> quondam filio
                                <persName><name ref="Parisius">Parisi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Albonellus">Albonelli</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Corsus">Corso</name></persName> quondam ***,
                                <persName><name ref="Heinricus/Denia">Enrigus
                            Denie</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Pincius/Deotisalvi"
                                >Pinchino Deotisalvi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Guerrus">Guerri</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Hugolinus/Georgius">Ugolinello Georgi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Bartholomaeus">Bartholomeus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Greca">Greche</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Parisius">Parisi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Teudaldus">Tedaldini</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Talliafecia">Talliafecia</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Torellus">Torelli</name></persName> germani et
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Tiniosus">Tiniosi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Wizo">Guittoni</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Albonellus">Albonelli</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Bonaiutus">Bonaiuto</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Aiutus">Aiuto</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Ferro">Ferro</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Baronte">Baroti</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Canamela">Canamele</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Balduinus Sesmondi">Baldono Sesmondi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Balduinus">Baldoino</name></persName>. Persone
                        onis (sic) suprascripti iuraverunt sicut supra dictum est. Dominice
                        incarnationis anno millesimo centesimo octuagesimo primo, sexto kalendas
                        iunii, indictione tertiadecima. Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Giselbertus">Guisalbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ibi fui et vidi et hoc totum scripsi.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
